name: Pesto Pasta
description: This classic Italian dish is made with fresh basil pesto, spaghetti, and cherry tomatoes.

name: Chicken Tikka Masala
description: This spicy Indian dish features marinated chicken in a creamy tomato-based sauce, served over rice.

name: Beef Stroganoff
description: This hearty Russian dish features tender strips of beef in a rich mushroom and sour cream sauce, served over egg noodles.

name: Caprese Salad
description: This refreshing Italian salad is made with fresh mozzarella cheese, ripe tomatoes, and basil leaves, drizzled with balsamic vinegar and olive oil.

name: Grilled Salmon
description: This healthy dish features a tender and flaky grilled salmon fillet, served with a side of roasted vegetables.

name: Vegetable Curry
description: This flavorful Indian dish features a variety of vegetables in a spicy and aromatic curry sauce, served over rice or with naan bread.

name: Taco Salad
description: This Tex-Mex inspired salad features seasoned ground beef, fresh lettuce, tomatoes, and corn, topped with crispy tortilla chips and a tangy dressing.

name: Lemon Garlic Shrimp
description: This flavorful seafood dish features succulent shrimp in a zesty lemon and garlic sauce, served over a bed of rice or pasta.
